# Rossmann Prophet Forecast API

This project demonstrates a **time series forecasting API** for Rossmann stores using **Prophet**, with deployment on **Render**. The project also integrates MLOps practices, Dockerization, and CI/CD pipelines with **GitHub Actions**.

